    Class Factory<TObject>

    Abstract implementation of IFactory<TCreate> that supports lifetime management using .

    Syntax
    public abstract class Factory<TObject> : IFactory<TObject>
    Type Parameters
    Name Description
    TObject

    The type of the instance to create.
    Remarks

    The internals will handle the lifetime management based on the value of the FactoryMode property. Instances are actually created using the abstract CreateInstance() and CreateInstance(Object[]) members, which needs to be implemented by the inheritor.
